review_data: Reviewed in the United States on July 9, 2022
name: Scott Erdman
title: Made the grandkids happy with a fire and smores.
review: Very nice set, worked great for us, more sturdy than other sets we have used.Look like these will last us awhile.Grand kids love to use these on our fire pit for Hot dogs and Marshmallows.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on May 1, 2022
name: J. Upton
title: Sturdy and well-made
review: We had previously bought “cheaper” sticks from Amazon only to have to return them because they were flimsy junk.We returned those and decided we’d spend the extra money and try these and so glad we did.Only sorry we didn’t order them first.They’re very sturdy and well-made.I have no doubt we’ll have them forever and a day.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on April 4, 2022
name: Larry
title: Very very nice.
review: These open fire roasting sticks are the best I’ve found. The length is adjustable so your hand stays cool. They are double pronged so hot dogs stay on. Strong and well made. Plus they came in a well made storage bag. I definitely recommend these.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 25, 2022
name: BTS
title: A Bit Pricey, But Nice
review: Bought these because they were sturdier than the wire roasting forks, but leaner than the heavier "hotdog" roasting forks.I feel they are a bit too pricey for the product, and a couple of the forks arrived with the tack-welding joints already separated.Overall, these would be a great item for about half that price... but there are few options like this out there.They did work well, and do the job intended though.
